  "prompt": "What can you say about my birth chart ?",
  "response": "I'd be happy to help interpret your birth chart! A birth chart, also known as a natal chart, is a snapshot of the sky at the exact moment and location of your birth. It maps the positions of the Sun, Moon, planets, and other celestial points, each influencing different aspects of your personality, emotions, and life experiences.\n\nTo provide a detailed and accurate interpretation, I'll need the following information:\n\n1. **Date of Birth** (month, day, year)\n2. **Time of Birth** (exact time is important for precise chart calculation)\n3. **Place of Birth** (city and country)\n\nIf you provide these details, I can offer insights into your Sun sign, Moon sign, Ascendant (Rising sign), and the positions of other planets in your chart, along with what they might mean for you. If you prefer not to share specific details, I can also explain the general components of a birth chart and how they influence different areas of life.\n\nFeel free to share the information you're comfortable with, and I'll do my best to assist you!",
